TreasureCollection.Name: Queen's Golden Ring
TreasureCollection.Description: The Queen's Golden Ring has been passed down for generations. It is thought to originally be a gift to the royal family by the King Alexander.

Quests.Title: Freshest Bodies
Quests.Description: Bring me the freshest bodies you find. I would like 5.

Quests.Title: Spooky Season
Quests.Description: I want you to bring me some skeletons. 10 of them should suffice.
